126 // This is the BIG function.
127 // It enters all primitives in the hash table.
128 Hashtab::Hashtab() {
129  hash_used = hash_size;
130  hash_usage = 0;
131  for (auto &k : eqtb) k.reset();
132  frozen_undef_token = nohash_primitive("undefined", CmdChr(undef_cmd, zero_code));
133  temp_token = nohash_primitive("temp", CmdChr(undef_cmd, zero_code));
134  endv_token = nohash_primitive("endv", CmdChr(endv_cmd, zero_code));
135  frozen_protection = nohash_primitive("frozen_cs", CmdChr(undef_cmd, zero_code));
136  frozen_endcsname = nohash_primitive("endcsname", CmdChr(endcsname_cmd, zero_code));
137 
138  iterate_token = nohash_primitive("iterate", CmdChr(undef_cmd, zero_code));
139  frozen_relax_token = nohash_primitive("relax", CmdChr(relax_cmd, relax_code));
140  eof_token = nohash_primitive("eof", CmdChr(eof_marker_cmd, zero_code));
141  Token *T = my_mathfont_table.data();
142  T[0] = primitive("mml@font@normal", mathfont_cmd, math_f_normal);
143  T[1] = primitive("mml@font@upright", mathfont_cmd, math_f_upright);
144  T[2] = primitive("mml@font@bold", mathfont_cmd, math_f_bold);
145  T[3] = primitive("mml@font@italic", mathfont_cmd, math_f_italic);
146  T[4] = primitive("mml@font@bolditalic", mathfont_cmd, math_f_bold_italic);
147  T[5] = primitive("mml@font@script", mathfont_cmd, math_f_script);
148  T[6] = primitive("mml@font@boldscript", mathfont_cmd, math_f_bold_script);
149  T[7] = primitive("mml@font@fraktur", mathfont_cmd, math_f_fraktur);
150  T[8] = primitive("mml@font@doublestruck", mathfont_cmd, math_f_doublestruck);
151  T[9] = primitive("mml@font@boldfraktur", mathfont_cmd, math_f_bold_fraktur);
152  T[10] = primitive("mml@font@sansserif", mathfont_cmd, math_f_sansserif);
153  T[11] = primitive("mml@font@boldsansserif", mathfont_cmd, math_f_bold_sansserif);
154  T[12] = primitive("mml@font@sansserifitalic", mathfont_cmd, math_f_sansserif_italic);
155  T[13] = primitive("mml@font@sansserifbolditalic", mathfont_cmd, math_f_sansserif_bold_italic);
156  T[14] = primitive("mml@font@monospace", mathfont_cmd, math_f_monospace);
157 
158  // now all tokens, in the order of their command codes.

170  primitive("anchorlabel", label_cmd, two_code);
171  ref_token = primitive("ref", ref_cmd);

173  primitive("XMLref", eqref_cmd);
174  par_token = primitive("par", par_cmd);

176  primitive("indent", start_par_cmd, one_code);
177  endcsname_token = primitive("endcsname", endcsname_cmd);
178  primitive("multicolumn", multicolumn_cmd);
179  frozen_dont_expand = nohash_primitive("notexpanded:", CmdChr(dont_expand_cmd, zero_code));
